// HTTP Native Server Test

: main
    L server 🛰️ 0 "8081"
    . 📤 1 "Server started on 8081\n"

    L req1 📥 ⚓ server
    L path1 🛰️ 2 ⚓ req1
    L suffix1 ⧉ ⚓ path1 "\n"
    L log1 ⧉ "Received request for: " ⚓ suffix1
    . 📤 1 ⚓ log1
    . 📤 ⮞ req1 "Hello from llmlang server"

    L req2 📥 ⚓ server
    L path2 🛰️ 2 ⚓ req2
    L suffix2 ⧉ ⚓ path2 "\n"
    L log2 ⧉ "Received request for: " ⚓ suffix2
    . 📤 1 ⚓ log2
    . 📤 ⮞ req2 "{\"status\":\"ok\"}"

    . 🛰️ 4 ⮞ server
    0

